Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:41.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi, in an attempt to\Nstop an orchestrated rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,decides to talk with the\Nleader of the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruined Erumalu behind her,\Nshe now heads straight for Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spiders Café at 8 O'Clock--\NThe Enemy Leaders Gather"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did your brother give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's just a scrap of paper.\N--Just a scrap of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is just a scrap of paper.\NIt's not even a note or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give me your hat, Luffy!\N--Huh? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that important, I'll sew it to\Nthe underside of your hat ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Great! Sew it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you go!\N--Thanks! Now I don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing written on it.\NWhat point is there to keeping it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace told me to keep it, so I'm keeping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your confidence isn't based on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? It's right a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't know about that...\N--Someone carry me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Yuba is just over those big rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make one more push to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yuba, huh?!\N--Yep! Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Carry me, Zoro...\N--Don't be a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ooh! Carry me too, Zoro!\N--Rock-paper-scissors, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation will commence\Nat high noon two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished the arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everything has gone smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150 Billions are on standby in Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also called Mr. 2 back.\NIt appears he failed to capture Mr. 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The officer agents' gathering is at\N8:00 tonight, at the Spiders Café...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is past 5:00 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume they'll start\Ngathering around now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes!\NMerry Christmas! Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a long, exhausting trip!\NMy back's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:10.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss Merry Christmas"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! It's all your fault, Mr. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your slowness is backache-inducing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! How's business, Paula?\NThe place is empty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place empty! Plempty! Ple! It's ple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.\NWelcome, Miss Merry Christmas, Mr. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Paula"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the shop all to yourselves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make you some orange pekoe\Nand... apple tea, was it, Mr. 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the hot drinks! I want\Nsomething I can drink right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some right away! Right away!\NRight now! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem lively. How is work going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my trade, screw up and you die!\NThings are going great, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You imbecile! Imbecile! Imbe! Imb! Im!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--? What kind of crazy\Nsongs does this place play now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Song? No, I have a sonata playing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your fingertip with your nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep with your fingernails!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before... being born...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson! Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love... and mascara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mascara with a nosebleed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm self-made!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:07:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So... Lesson!\N--Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lesson!\N--Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, the greatest!\N--The greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are deux lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not stupid, Paula!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One Octopar, please!\N--Octopar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! An Octopus\NParfait! Everyone knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, you guys can leave now!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lazy with your dance practice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Un, deux! Un, deux...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Fatty! Old hag! You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap, you! Pipe down,\Nyou're hurting my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, I hear even\NMr. 1's team is being mobilized!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met 'em for whatever\Nreason, so I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The night grows ever later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the appointed time of 8:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored I spin around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll take a spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! You're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, hag?!\NYou wanna fight or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now! Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, now! What happened to you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come bursting back in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... It was him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. They're acquaintances of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were acting suspiciously\Nin the desert, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I doubt they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be on rather close terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but worthless, cozy relationships\Nwill only result in your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These men are my subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mr. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, Deux, Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, Deux, Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un! Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! He slipped through the wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He shattered the wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! That's enough, Mr. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, Miss Doublefinger.\NI'm going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Let go of me, Fatty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2! Cool your anger as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now 8:00. All the agents\Nthat should be here are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a letter with orders has\Narrived at the Spiders Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're to head to Rainbase,\Nthe city of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man we call boss, the man\Nwhose face we've never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is waiting for us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be on their\Nway here to Rainbase now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Bunchi to get them. I expect\Nthem to arrive sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you were\Nactually Miss Doublefinger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss Doublefinger"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever saying that I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found replacements for\Nthe Billions wiped out in Nanohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished assigning the replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dispatched the Lizard Runners\Nto contact the new Billions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Everything is progressing smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up ahead! I see a light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we make it to Yuba?!\NI can't really see with all this sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that sound be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city doesn't look right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of Yuba is being\Nstruck by a sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. It's almost no\Ndifferent from that Erumalu city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this supposed to be\Nan oasis city, Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand has raised the ground!\NThe oasis has been swallowed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you travelers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted from\Nyour trek through the desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. This town is a bit dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're free to rest here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of inns here.\NThey are this town's pride, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, we came because we heard\Nthe rebel army was in this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you\Nhave with the rebel army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! Don't tell me you're\Nhoping to join the rebellion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for those fools,\Nthey left town long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sandstorm hit the town just now,\Nbut it certainly wasn't the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand has dried up\Nafter three years of drought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sandstorms began to\Nfrequent this town ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, the oasis of\Nthe past was swallowed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving what you see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the town's flow of supplies gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not even the rebel army's protracted\Nstruggle would have worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rebel army moved its base to Katorea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katorea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that, Vivi?! Is Katorea close by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an oasis next to Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katorea is the town where\NI got lost and met Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When you saved me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lashes says he was carrying\Nrebel army goods to Katorea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why didn't you say so sooner!\N--Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whatever!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we come all this way, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "Vivi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, old guy! Vivi isn't the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell him that, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan? Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I can't blame you.\NI did lose some weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto-ojisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Vivi-chan. This is goodbye for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit sometime,\Nonce the city's taken shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Toto-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba will surely make this kingdom lusher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto-ojisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan. I have faith in His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone who would\Never betray the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rebellion is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if it hasn't rained\Nfor a mere three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in His Majesty.\NMost of the country still does, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many times I tried to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they won't listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebellion won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their strength is at its limit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to settle things\Nonce and for all in the next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:19:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their backs are to the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Vivi-chan! Stop those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:25.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's our leader?\N--Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Toto-ojisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will stop the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Vivi-chan. This is goodbye for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit sometime,\Nonce the city's taken shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Toto-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make an awesome city
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make this kingdom even lusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Vivi! Grow up to be a great princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've contacted everyone in the other towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. The time to strike has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We don't have nearly\Nenough weapons, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no other choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who can\Nprotect this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands, and the sand\Nand time that spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is what\NI was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kick Crocodile's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really knows how to get\Nstraight to the point sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! You want it so nobody dies in this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you think that's soft-hearted?\N--Hold on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least put all our lives on the line together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy vs. Vivi! The Tearful Vow\Nto Put Friends on the Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
